c effects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/17351/', '', 'Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, Tryptophan, Levomilnacipran, Vilazodone', 'Azelastine, Ketotifen, Desloratadine', 1767369485);
